---
title: Char-Broiled BBQ Chicken with Summery Potato and Green Bean Salad
description: Nothing says summer like BBQ! That’s why we’re kicking off the season with one of our favourite summertime dishes: BBQ chicken and potato salad! We’re dressing this potato salad up with fresh basil and crisp green beans. If you have a grill, it's great to use for this recipe instead of the broiler.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/char-broiled-bbq-chicken-c811be01.jpg
